      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782663158825,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Batching\n\nData is batched when sending to MQ. Usually on producer end\n\nHigh batch size = high throughput\nlow batch size = low latency\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Batching\n\nData is batched when sending to MQ. Usually on producer end\n\nHigh batch size = high throughput\nlow batch size = low latency\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
