      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Push vs pull for consumers\n\npush : MQ push data to consumer\npro:\nlow latency\ncon:\nconsumer can be overwhelmed\n\npull : consumers pull data from MQ\npro:\nconsumer pulls data at its pace\ncon:\nif no data, consumer still pulls\nbetter , cause consumer can pull data at its own pace\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Push vs pull for consumers\n\npush : MQ push data to consumer\npro:\nlow latency\ncon:\nconsumer can be overwhelmed\n\npull : consumers pull data from MQ\npro:\nconsumer pulls data at its pace\ncon:\nif no data, consumer still pulls\nbetter , cause consumer can pull data at its own pace\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
